column5: We are leaving Friday for Eagle Lake, will be fishing around Nasha Bay. Anyone been on that lake lately hows the fishing? Also any other areas that we should look at on the lake. Thanks

Good luck with your trip. Will be going the following friday for the first time. We will be by Sportsman Bay, not to far from your area. I posted back in June sometime with only 1 responce,good luck. Burdman
